skdetail:
Flash Briefing Skill
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
des: This flash briefing provides you with the latest episode of the Slovak daily news podcast by SME - Dobré ráno. Every morning you can start your day with top news briefing and go deep on one specific topic.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
